{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb9cb70994","title":"西北野战军羊力迅速南进相机攻占洛川等城","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4947bb2313","index":0,"year":1947,"month":9,"day":2,"articleId":"cb9cb70994"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ee205452f1","type":"paragraph","text":"西北野战军羊力迅速南进相机攻占洛川等城","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"cb9cb70994"},{"id":"a2c02d18a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年9月2日）彭，并告贺、习世日命令限好。乘敌二十九军在来脂地区排狗犹豫，我军以一部节节阻敌，主力迅遗南进（避开一切强固据点）：相机攻占洛川、中部、宜君、同官、耀县、三原、蒲城、白水、富平及黄河以东、消水以北各城，开辟战场（背靠贯龙山），解决冬衣，扩大兵源是可能的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"cb9cb70994"},{"id":"27e353ffca","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"cb9cb70994"},{"id":"a0b16ef3d2","type":"paragraph","text":"二日十二时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给西北野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。[2]贺、习，指贺龙、习件融，当时分别任陕甘宁晋线联防军司令员和政治委员。3]指1947年8月31日彭德怀对西北野战军发布的命令。每令说，无[4]中部，旧县名，即今陕西黄陵。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"cb9cb70994"}],"page":{"id":"a86e299412","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"cb9cb70994","start":256,"end":256}}}},"__N_SSG":true}